means more honest answers.

156
00:07:20,086 --> 00:07:21,388
- Max... Max!
- Iggy.

157
00:07:21,488 --> 00:07:22,925
If we're not improving,
we're failing.

158
00:07:23,009 --> 00:07:24,992
