- Thank you.

218
00:09:57,791 --> 00:09:59,789
- Are these the new surveys?
- Sure are. There you go.

219
00:09:59,873 --> 00:10:02,015
And remember,
complete candour is welcome.

220
00:10:02,115 --> 00:10:04,188
And for you.

221
00:10:04,438 --> 00:10:07,353
